/svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 21, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104lyg1665702836847.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/lyg1665702836847.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/lyg1665702836847.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"lyg1665702836847\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                     \n Open ... \n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"lyg1665702836847__open_34612\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Create or open a library or object in a library.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lyg1665702836847__p_d9908e1_d9909e1_d9910e1\">The upper part of the dialog box displays the currently selected object. The lower part displays a tree of objects at the same level.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lyg1665702836847__p_d9911e1_d9912e1_d9913e1\">Double-click an object to open it or to expand or collapse related objects.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"lyg1665702836847__topic_d8017e1_d8018e1_d8019e1_d8020e1_d8021e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d280953e63\">\n                       \n Icons\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lyg1665702836847__p_d9917e1_d9918e1_d9919e1\">Buttons in the upper right corner of the form enable you to create, retrieve, and navigate to objects.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"lyg1665702836847__table_d1031e1_d1032e1_d1033e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Icons used in the Open form</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"lyg1665702836847__table_d1031e1_d1032e1_d1033e1__entry__1\">\n Icon\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"lyg1665702836847__table_d1031e1_d1032e1_d1033e1__entry__2\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lyg1665702836847__table_d1031e1_d1032e1_d1033e1__entry__1\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"lyg1665702836847__fig_w147ab1b7b7b5b3b7b1b1b1_w148ab1b7b7b5b3b7b1b1_w149ab1b7b7b5b3b7b1_w150ab1b7b7b5b3b7_w151ab1b7b7b5b3_w152ab1b7b7b5_w153ab1b7b7_w154ab1b7_w155ab1\">\n<img alt=\"Create new object\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/u_new.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lyg1665702836847__table_d1031e1_d1032e1_d1033e1__entry__2\">\n Create a new object\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lyg1665702836847__table_d1031e1_d1032e1_d1033e1__entry__1\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"lyg1665702836847__fig_w156ab1b7b7b5b3b7b3b1b1_w157ab1b7b7b5b3b7b3b1_w158ab1b7b7b5b3b7b3_w159ab1b7b7b5b3b7_w160ab1b7b7b5b3_w161ab1b7b7b5_w162ab1b7b7_w163ab1b7_w164ab1\">\n<img alt='Retrieve objects\"' class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/u_retrieve.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lyg1665702836847__table_d1031e1_d1032e1_d1033e1__entry__2\">\n Retrieve objects\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lyg1665702836847__table_d1031e1_d1032e1_d1033e1__entry__1\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"lyg1665702836847__fig_w165ab1b7b7b5b3b7b5b1b1_w166ab1b7b7b5b3b7b5b1_w167ab1b7b7b5b3b7b5_w168ab1b7b7b5b3b7_w169ab1b7b7b5b3_w170ab1b7b7b5_w171ab1b7b7_w172ab1b7_w173ab1\">\n<img alt=\"Clear form\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/u_clear.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lyg1665702836847__table_d1031e1_d1032e1_d1033e1__entry__2\">\n Clear the form\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lyg1665702836847__table_d1031e1_d1032e1_d1033e1__entry__1\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"lyg1665702836847__fig_w174ab1b7b7b5b3b7b7b1b1_w175ab1b7b7b5b3b7b7b1_w176ab1b7b7b5b3b7b7_w177ab1b7b7b5b3b7_w178ab1b7b7b5b3_w179ab1b7b7b5_w180ab1b7b7_w181ab1b7_w182ab1\">\n<img alt=\"Select parent\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/u_up.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lyg1665702836847__table_d1031e1_d1032e1_d1033e1__entry__2\">\n Select objects one level higher (double-click the icon for the top-level object in the upper part of the form)\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lyg1665702836847__p_d9920e1_d9921e1_d9922e1\">When creating or editing menus, the following buttons are also shown in the Open dialog. Select an icon to display the list of available menus of that type in the selected library.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"lyg1665702836847__table_d1034e1_d1035e1_d1036e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Icons used in the Open form for Menus</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"lyg1665702836847__table_d1034e1_d1035e1_d1036e1__entry__1\">\n Icon\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"lyg1665702836847__table_d1034e1_d1035e1_d1036e1__entry__2\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lyg1665702836847__table_d1034e1_d1035e1_d1036e1__entry__1\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"lyg1665702836847__fig_w183ab1b7b7b9b3b7b1b1b1_w184ab1b7b7b9b3b7b1b1_w185ab1b7b7b9b3b7b1_w186ab1b7b7b9b3b7_w187ab1b7b7b9b3_w188ab1b7b7b9_w189ab1b7b7_w190ab1b7_w191ab1\">\n<img alt=\"Menu bar icon\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/u7_menbar.gif?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lyg1665702836847__table_d1034e1_d1035e1_d1036e1__entry__2\">\n Display or create menu bars\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lyg1665702836847__table_d1034e1_d1035e1_d1036e1__entry__1\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"lyg1665702836847__fig_w192ab1b7b7b9b3b7b3b1b1_w193ab1b7b7b9b3b7b3b1_w194ab1b7b7b9b3b7b3_w195ab1b7b7b9b3b7_w196ab1b7b7b9b3_w197ab1b7b7b9_w198ab1b7b7_w199ab1b7_w200ab1\">\n<img alt=\"Popup menu icon\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/u7_menpop.gif?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lyg1665702836847__table_d1034e1_d1035e1_d1036e1__entry__2\">\n Display or create pop-up menus\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lyg1665702836847__table_d1034e1_d1035e1_d1036e1__entry__1\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"lyg1665702836847__fig_w201ab1b7b7b9b3b7b5b1b1_w202ab1b7b7b9b3b7b5b1_w203ab1b7b7b9b3b7b5_w204ab1b7b7b9b3b7_w205ab1b7b7b9b3_w206ab1b7b7b9_w207ab1b7b7_w208ab1b7_w209ab1\">\n<img alt=\"Drop-down menu icon\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/u7_mencom.gif?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lyg1665702836847__table_d1034e1_d1035e1_d1036e1__entry__2\">\n Display or create drop-down menus\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"lyg1665702836847__topic_d8022e1_d8023e1_d8024e1_d8025e1_d8026e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d280953e243\">\n                       \n How to\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lyg1665702836847__li_d4535e1_d4536e1_d4537e1\">Enter the name of the object to open it, if it already exists, or to create it. If an object of that name does not exist, you will be prompted to create it.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lyg1665702836847__li_d4538e1_d4539e1_d4540e1\">Alternatively:\n <ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lyg1665702836847__li_d4541e1_d4542e1_d4543e1\">To open an object, select it in the list of objects displayed.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lyg1665702836847__li_d4544e1_d4545e1_d4546e1\">To create a new object, click the <img alt=\"Create new object\" class=\"image\" id=\"lyg1665702836847__image_lrc_vvl_5cc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/u_new.png?_LANG=enus\"/>  icon, and enter the name of the new object. </li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529786\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529786\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Open ... Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 21, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Open ... Create or open a library or object in a library. The upper part of the dialog box displays the currently selected object. The lower part displays a tree of objects at the same level. Double-click an object to open it or to expand or collapse related objects. Icons Buttons in the upper right corner of the form enable you to create, retrieve, and navigate to objects. Table 1. Icons used in the Open form Icon Meaning Create a new object Retrieve objects Clear the form Select objects one level higher (double-click the icon for the top-level object in the upper part of the form) When creating or editing menus, the following buttons are also shown in the Open dialog. Select an icon to display the list of available menus of that type in the selected library. Table 2. Icons used in the Open form for Menus Icon Meaning Display or create menu bars Display or create pop-up menus Display or create drop-down menus How to Enter the name of the object to open it, if it already exists, or to create it. If an object of that name does not exist, you will be prompted to create it. Alternatively: To open an object, select it in the list of objects displayed. To create a new object, click the icon, and enter the name of the new object. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}